text: Belskoye () is a rural locality (a selo) in Alataninsky Selsoviet, Sterlitamaksky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,144 as of 2010. There are 9 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Sterlitamak, 5 km from Alatana. == References == Category:Rural localities in Sterlitamaksky District
title: Belskoye, Republic of Bashkortostan
